sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Worker as L4 ReAct Worker
    participant Redis as StateDB (Redis)
    participant Kafka as Observer Log (Kafka)
    participant Archiver as Archiver Service
    participant MySQL as Cold Storage (MySQL)

    Note over Worker, MySQL: 1. 正常推演步骤 (Shadow Sync & Observer Log)
    Worker->>Redis: RPUSH 完整快照 (Append-only)
    Worker->>Kafka: 异步发送 Thought/Action 事件
    Worker->>MySQL: 写入 mao_task_log (含 state_digest)
    
    Note over Kafka, MySQL: 2. 异步流式归档
    Kafka-->>Archiver: 消费审计事件
    Archiver->>MySQL: 批量更新/插入审计明细 (幂等)

    Note over Worker, MySQL: 3. 任务挂起触发深冻结 (Deep Freeze)
    Worker->>Worker: 触发 ASYNC 技能，状态变更为 SUSPENDED
    Worker->>Redis: 获取当前全量快照
    Worker->>MySQL: 写入 mao_task_snapshot_archive (持久化)
    Worker->>Worker: 销毁当前线程，释放资源

    Note over Archiver, MySQL: 4. 兜底迁移策略 (TTL 预警)
    Archiver->>Redis: 扫描 TTL < 10% 的挂起快照
    Archiver->>MySQL: 强制归档至 task_snapshot_archive
    Archiver->>Redis: 释放 Redis 内存，仅留索引 Key

    Note over Worker, MySQL: 5. 审计回溯重构 (Reconstruct)
    Archiver->>Redis: 优先尝试读取全量快照
    alt Redis 命中
        Redis-->>Archiver: 返回完整脑电图
    else Redis 缺失 (过期或宕机)
        Archiver->>MySQL: 读取 task_log (state_digest) + snapshot_archive
        MySQL-->>Archiver: 返回部分/重组脑电图 (is_complete: false)
    end
